deem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=7478b8d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n《以下夠數，到期前越多越好，踩多腳無人嫌多》<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n8) 請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案，向林鄭的所謂讓步說「不了」<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=0e5aa7b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n9)請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1e4a878e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n10)請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1340f292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020</a><br />\n<br />\n11)要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=194f6f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations</a> <br />\n<br />\n簽署＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞Share 10個朋友簽</span>"},{"pid":"acf57cdc21a12597e05a15e1d997bf4f46fb4cd0","tid":1558470,"uid":128994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"662816fea3bbfc53b722c912e249682c2c814824","tid":1558470,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df625d55b8b8ca89abf1e891845ac4c93b225496","tid":1558470,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"正式發佈 9月11日示威者向美國悼念日文宣 大家今晚12點前要對全世界宣傳好！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558607</a>"},{"pid":"72e8b5e00fa70d759915f7e1970e0fb1b8481eb9","tid":1558470,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be2db2d4fabaf9e723c60346737a92618cf77d66","tid":1558470,"uid":237207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECSjASM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECSjASM.jpg&h=e1425070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：9月15日<br />\n時間：下午三時正<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n（不反對通知書申請中）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n我知道大家都好攰 大家都好驚 但係只要人多 其實就會安全 我唔信200萬人係港島夠膽終止個遊行！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有堅持 才有勝利</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">非看見勝利 才走堅持</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我們一起走下去，將來煲底見！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"樓主可以貼過去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1558668/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1558668/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2d9bea71e173f56d565b49102ca0093ad3a855eb","tid":1558470,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:02:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646fc1d190c29d0accbd6fa3f19f6d154d72e7f5","tid":1558470,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"466d95441d0f82283b799f0b7adf4453fc9dde4c","tid":1558470,"uid":56305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"推！ 一人整一張"},{"pid":"5c11f002be4e29046e459af90a81767dc0c90436","tid":1558470,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"行動post 推呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d54304598f6c4d76b8da472524cf53b278ea112","tid":1558470,"uid":111613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"491de9d817775d443cdb7d5f3dd6a38d8d55